CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Baosheng Media Group Holdings Ltd operates as a V-log streaming marketing service provider. The firm offers comprehensive marketing solutions. Its services are Internet effect marketing, V-log or short video streaming marketing including content production and operation, e-commerce marketing, original big data platform system service, and AI technology. It provides one-stop and full-link deep customized marketing solutions for partners. Baosheng Group is also a core agency of domestic Internet companies such as Tencent, Alibaba, Bytedance, and Kuaishou, with performing channel marketing services, technologies, and applications.
